Release 2013/11/29

	1.  Updated source packages to use generics.  Therefore requires 
	Java 1.5 or better.
	
	2.  Bug fix: NullPointer exception when putting a Date object to
	a DateField object.
	
	3.  Cleaned up date parsing logic in DateField class.
	
	4.  Cleaned up some testing modules.
	
	5.  Added addFields(ArrayList<Fields>) to DBF class.
	
	6.  Improved Swing dbfViewer class.
	
		6.1  Added Exit menu item.
		
		6.2  Added logic to test data changes. Includes new dialog
		requesting continue if data has changed when opening a new dbf
		or exiting the application.

